Migration Helpers
#################

Add and remove foreign key restraints for MySQL tables.

To use add
  require 'migration_helpers'

on top of your migration files, and then
  extend MigrationHelpers

right after the migration class definition

See the lib/migration_helpers.rb file for details on usage of the methods:
  add_foreign_key
  remove_foreign_key

